<p>The star explained that she is currently carrying one of her very first Birkin bags she purchased, after her mom Kris Jenner told her to buy it.</p>

<p>'Surprisingly Kris Jenner told me to buy the bag,' adding: 'Because its the So Black edition and they are really rare. She was like there's this bag available. You need it. These bags are great investments.'</p>

